                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-text">"I was nervous about leaving my cat with a sitter, but Mark was amazing! He sent photos and updates daily, and my cat was so happy when I returned."</p>
                </div>
